# Tools and Standards

## Recommended Tools for Development

- [PHPStorm](https://www.jetbrains.com/phpstorm/)
- [SublimeText](https://www.sublimetext.com)
- [WPCS](https://github.com/WordPress/WordPress-Coding-Standards)
- [Plugin Boilerplate](https://github.com/TukuToi/better-wp-plugin-boilerplate)

## Standards

- ClassicPress follows the (WordPress) [Coding Standards](http://codex.wordpress.org/WordPress_Coding_Standards) and [Documentation Standards](https://make.wordpress.org/core/handbook/best-practices/inline-documentation-standards/php/).
- ClassicPress uses SemVer, and expects Plugins and Themes coded for ClassicPress to follow [SemVer](https://semver.org/) as well.
- ClassicPress will publish Changelogs following [these Standards](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/)
